cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper proposes a method for image recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method involves learning a discriminative block-diagonal representation, which involves optimization and machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on several image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
